{"tid":1177540,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"誰是誰非，求拍教","createTime":"2019-05-29T21:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T08:20:27.000Z","uid":168607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe48c297db4d9b547c489e300184e4d0c83d4d34","tid":1177540,"uid":168607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T21:41:09.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ptN8jdR_vdo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FptN8jdR_vdo&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=8f4408c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ptN8jdR_vdo</a>"},{"pid":"f257851b1fdfdbe252db888fb9917d0ef3e07e7d","tid":1177540,"uid":16827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe48c297db4d9b547c489e300184e4d0c83d4d34","tid":1177540,"uid":168607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T21:41:09.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ptN8jdR_vdo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FptN8jdR_vdo&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=8f4408c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ptN8jdR_vdo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:28:15.000Z","msg":"仲咩唔剪輯先放上來，睇左你揸左4分鐘車先到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78155566e925902d4282e87c6bc500fd6bd53e4f","tid":1177540,"uid":16827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:31:17.000Z","msg":"Van 仔硬cut 埋來，就咁睇，應該係佢問題。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢都知衰，不過見師兄你咁好火，所以先忍唔住為左面子咁硬同你嘈，你見佢嘈到後期佢都縮就知，純粹為啖氣，道理係你到"},{"pid":"32b3881355ba1e166904e720aeb29fb8cd5774c0","tid":1177540,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />架貨van咁樣攝入黎仲要入得半條線 仲洗問?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e18a9c23761fbf0f5799c54f2f2275381bf8d9","tid":1177540,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:40:05.000Z","msg":"btw 下次cut一cut先<br />\n睇前面三分幾鐘我以為自己miss咗乜嘢精彩鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7677a3d743897259e40892c3c5dcd686a491fa3a","tid":1177540,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"燈位前有四條線<br />\n左一二線轉左去沙田市中心<br />\n右一二線轉右去尖山/大埔道/大圍<br />\n而家情況即係<br />\n二線轉三線<br />\nVan 仔一定要靠左攞左線<br />\n即係上尖山或轉入成全路工廠區方向<br />\n所以佢實錯<br />\n但貨車就要攞右線往大圍方向<br />\n不過你大車我當你偷位攞咗少少中線<br />\n唔好以為條中線一定係你嘅<br />\n二線轉三線<br />\n無人有中線嘅優先權<br />\n係咪好似有啲誤會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22028b599292c174966b56dda912ebc978a1e7e","tid":1177540,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"3:28開始"},{"pid":"6a936e9f0081285e37aa40e9777b802855176ccc","tid":1177540,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7677a3d743897259e40892c3c5dcd686a491fa3a","tid":1177540,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"燈位前有四條線<br />\n左一二線轉左去沙田市中心<br />\n右一二線轉右去尖山/大埔道/大圍<br />\n而家情況即係<br />\n二線轉三線<br />\nVan 仔一定要靠左攞左線<br />\n即係上尖山或轉入成全路工廠區方向<br />\n所以佢實錯<br />\n但貨車就要攞右線往大圍方向<br />\n不過你大車我當你偷位攞咗少少中線<br />\n唔好以為條中線一定係你嘅<br />\n二線轉三線<br />\n無人有中線嘅優先權<br />\n係咪好似有啲誤會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"第二度 copy 番嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMarkX Owner 先生：<br />\n<br />\n多謝你6月10日的電郵， 查詢交通燈路口轉彎事宜。本署現回覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n在交通燈轉右路口，如車輛由兩線行車路右轉往三線行車路，駛入三線行車路中線的優先權並不存在。而駕駛者轉彎時，應格外小心。留意車輛在道路上的位置及速度是否適當。提防車身較長的車輛在轉右時，須要橫越整個路面，才可轉彎。 <br />\n<br />\n在轉彎途中，因為駕駛人的視綫可能受其他車輛阻擋，應留意有沒有其他車輛駛近，而去選擇適合的行車線 ; 再者駕駛者不可切過道路的彎角。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你對道路安全的駕駛查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n運輸署署長 <br />\n(黃家聰 代行)"},{"pid":"13414c140b18c497cf8ae74fbf5292f8d1e062a3","tid":1177540,"uid":168607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思咁多位ching，我都係見無聊上youtube見到放上黎請教下，謝謝Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}